    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at dnata India",
    "description": "We at dnata India are looking for an experienced Revenue Manager based out of Lucknow. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout dnata India:\ndnata India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with dnata India!",
